name: Yoru ヨル (Chainsaw Man)
description:
Yoru ヨル (Chainsaw Man)

Triggers with yoru, works fine with weight 1.

Used Cetus-mix, Donko-mix, NeverEnding Dream and snapdd00 for example images.

Usage

General tags: yoru, 1girl, long hair, red eyes, scar on face, ringed eyes (v2)

yoru, 1girl, long hair, yellow eyes, scar on face, ringed eyes (v1Beta)

For her school uniform, use:

  • prompt: pinafore dress, black belt, black ribbon, black kneesocks, loafers

In v2, her black ribbon tend to leak into other outfits, but can usually be fixed by adding ((black ribbon, collar, pinafore dress:1.2)) in the negative prompt.

If you want Yoru's scar to extend to the nose as well, prompting scar on nose works most of the time.

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description:
• Re-trained with a dataset where Yoru is red-eyed.

  • Same parameters as v1.

modelVersions.name: v1_Beta
modelVersions.description:
• Trained on the NAI model, used Kohya-Dreambooth colab.

  • 4 batch size, 3 epochs.

  • 1.5e-5 text encoder LR

  • 1.5e-4 unet LR

  • 1e-5 optimizer LR

  • Training resolution 768x768.
